Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.07,0:00:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you see them?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.28,0:00:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.41,0:00:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see them yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.91,0:00:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I feel their presence.\NIt could happen at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.71,0:00:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are all the Octobrists \Nso fearful of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.51,0:00:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those northern freaks came many times...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.96,0:00:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but they have never breached this wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.88,0:00:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been driving them to the\Nother side for hundreds of years.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.89,0:00:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are the people of Carneades,\Nthe protectors of this wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.47,0:00:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What can those freaks do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.49,0:00:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those soldiers are useless.\NThey won't even last two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.56,0:00:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in charge here. I'm going\Nto Kafet to check on the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.12,0:01:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you talking about those two old men?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.70,0:01:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. If they don't lead the army,\Nthis country will be destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.00,0:01:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't win a battle like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.21,0:01:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The power of Drifters alone\Ncan't bring us a victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.18,0:02:47.27,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Act 3\NArmy of Ours--Sortie at Dawn"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.47,0:02:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be a fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.27,0:02:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you telling me to give up my command...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.37,0:02:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to those bizarre Drifters?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.15,0:02:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mess with me, magicians!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.65,0:02:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if we don't let them lead, we'll lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.19,0:03:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you mocking me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.07,0:03:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you know?!\NYou are just a magician organization!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.03,0:03:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, what can those two Drifters--\Nthose scruffy old men--do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.67,0:03:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What? What are you two arguing about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.96,0:03:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... umm... we're trying to have him\Ngive up command of his troops to you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.92,0:03:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! All of a sudden! That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.97,0:03:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know it's unreasonable, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.47,0:03:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...if you don't command them, we'll all die.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.80,0:03:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph. Why on earth do\Nwe have to do such a thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.18,0:03:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nasty Drifters!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.56,0:03:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Bastards!\N--Shut up, Drifters!\N--What the hell are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.95,0:03:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand their language,\Nbut I could tell we were insulted.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.28,0:03:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.90,0:03:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.53,0:03:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm about to pee my pants.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.53,0:03:45.78,Top Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Shiver shiver shiver"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.12,0:03:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Huh?!\N--You idiot! Hold it! You old fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.87,0:03:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I can't. Aging causes me to\Nhave sudden urges to urinate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.62,0:03:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Wh-What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.88,0:04:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fed up with this lightning of Carthage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.22,0:04:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I hate getting old...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.86,0:04:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is just a stupid old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.12,0:04:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I will give\Ncommand to such an old wretch!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.67,0:04:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.75,0:04:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That man is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.96,0:04:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...someone even millions of you can't defeat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.43,0:04:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That man... That man...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.54,0:04:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That man is Hannibal--Hannibal Barca!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.27,0:04:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Roman Empire did not fear
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.85,0:04:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet, facing that man alone,\NHannibal, did Rome tremble!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.85,0:04:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,any enemy, even if there \Nwere millions of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.81,0:05:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.73,0:05:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.82,0:05:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two, that's far enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.79,0:05:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if he gave in now, \Nit's already pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.95,0:05:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please get ready to escape.\NSoon, this place will descend into carnage.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.25,0:05:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Octobrists will also withdraw.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.17,0:05:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before the battle against\Nthe Black King's army begins,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.88,0:05:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we must allow the Drifters to escape...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.33,0:05:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...no matter what it takes\Nor whom we sacrifice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.88,0:05:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scipio...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.44,0:05:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.46,0:05:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, that's the assurance of the victor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.88,0:05:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I am stronger than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.56,0:05:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say, you beardless idiot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.22,0:05:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna fight, old man?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.98,0:05:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Semu. This is Semu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.20,0:05:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?\NWh... is... the... con... dition... ther...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.70,0:05:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ca... yo... hea... me, Gr... Mas...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.91,0:05:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's magic disruption.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.24,0:05:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot! They are coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.04,0:05:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no response from\Nfour reconnaissance units.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.00,0:06:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.00,0:06:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are those noises?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.21,0:06:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's goin' on?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.59,0:06:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got a cigarette?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.09,0:06:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be an idiot. Course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.30,0:06:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're lying! You're hiding the\Nlast two cigarettes, aren't ya?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.68,0:06:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whose fault was it that we\Nended up in a place like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.27,0:06:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who would give ya cigarettes, ya fool?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.81,0:06:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want a cigarette so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.44,0:06:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wherever we go, there's no tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.37,0:06:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We, the Wild Bunch, only got today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.91,0:06:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should at least be able \Nto smoke as I please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.62,0:06:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Black King...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.00,0:06:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.14,0:07:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crusade, crusade.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.56,0:07:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crusade of his Majesty, the Black King.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.94,0:07:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crusade, crusade.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.15,0:07:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time has finally come.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.57,0:07:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crusade, crusade.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.03,0:07:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who have ears, listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.24,0:07:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who have eyes, watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.62,0:07:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who have mouths, shout.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.30,0:07:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let them know everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.66,0:07:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crusade, crusade, crusade.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.50,0:07:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the beginning of\Nthe eradication of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.29,0:07:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gather together. Join us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.51,0:07:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All your power to the Black King!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.43,0:07:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All your power to the Black King!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.43,0:07:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Black King... The king of the "Ends."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.27,0:07:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.81,0:07:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's already here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.86,0:07:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you hate us that much, Black King?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.91,0:07:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The "Drifters," this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.28,0:07:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and everything else?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.87,0:08:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are coming! They're closing in!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.91,0:08:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Archers! Take aim!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.63,0:08:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring death.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.71,0:08:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.41,0:08:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hijikata.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.89,0:08:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Joan of Arc.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.94,0:08:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anastasia Nikolaevna Romanova.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.25,0:08:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You may go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.72,0:08:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At last, you've made your move.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.25,0:08:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really going to eradicate this world?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.76,0:08:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You do as you please.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.06,0:09:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. That's how I live my life.\NSo, allow me to continue on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.52,0:09:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurou Hougan Yoshitsune.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.77,0:09:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which side are you on...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.24,0:09:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the Drifters or the Ends?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.47,0:09:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see... Whichever interests me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.70,0:09:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot! Shoot! Fire at will!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.07,0:09:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let them close in! Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.38,0:09:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From Air Command to Dragon Cavalry.\NEngage in aerial support.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.34,0:09:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deploy mobile aerial forces!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.07,0:09:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! They're coming one\Nafter another. There is no end!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.19,0:09:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Descend! Begin Operation Draborne!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.53,0:10:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Descent successful. Minimum damage.\N2nd platoon, ready up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.16,0:10:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Go! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.94,0:10:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From Agnela 1 of Air Command\Nto Dragon Cavalry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.23,0:10:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Backup requested by the Goblin 7th battalion.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.69,0:10:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coordinates, 42-7-12-73-42-8.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.74,0:10:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too late. We can't save them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.99,0:10:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if a way for the Drifters \Nto escape exists...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.93,0:11:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which one...?! Which one?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.27,0:11:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which one...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.48,0:11:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which one?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.07,0:11:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?! Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.03,0:11:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit! Shit! What the hell has just happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.07,0:11:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"August 1, 1945, Kanno\NDestroyer Naoshi Captain"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.91,0:11:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Who told you to stop?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.92,0:11:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run! You piece of shit! Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.67,0:11:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.68,0:11:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.43,0:11:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?! Is this fuckin' Uzumasa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.31,0:11:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where the fuck am I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.90,0:12:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...?! You moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.61,0:12:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the shit?! Why the hell are\Nyou riding on a dragon, you idiot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.69,0:12:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where the shit am I?!\NDon't mess with me, you jackass!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.50,0:12:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Which one is he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.29,0:12:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No clue! For now, the Drifters'\Nevacuation must be...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.82,0:12:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Northern Wall was torn down!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.66,0:12:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Bring more troops here now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.93,0:12:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But it's too...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.21,0:13:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hot... So hot.\NI feel like my body is on fire...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.61,0:13:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Burn them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.43,0:13:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything... Burn them all to ash.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.06,0:13:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drift in the air. Float \Non the water's surface!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.86,0:13:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Burn! Burn!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.74,0:13:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything in this world\Nshould be burned to ash!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.20,0:13:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.24,0:13:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What on earth?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.09,0:13:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sleep, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.68,0:13:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.19,0:14:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You... bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.65,0:14:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fuckin' jackass!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.78,0:14:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Open up! Open the gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.03,0:14:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't get it open. It's frozen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.20,0:14:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May I defrost it for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.92,0:15:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kill them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.52,0:15:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They still ain't here.\NHey, it isn't looking good, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.44,0:15:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not good. Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.53,0:15:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we leave without 'em?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.66,0:15:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way. Hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.28,0:15:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--They're here.\N--Please get on quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.62,0:15:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll catch up with you later.\NGet going, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.42,0:15:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are those two old men going to be our cargo?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.54,0:15:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.09,0:15:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are ya dressed like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.30,0:15:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say, punk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.30,0:15:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing more that can be done here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.60,0:15:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Northern Wall,"\Nthe Kingdom of Carneades, has fallen!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.43,0:16:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scipio! Hannibal!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.77,0:16:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be disturbed by our sudden
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.93,0:16:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,request to fight so soon after your arrival.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.36,0:16:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... But please help us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.49,0:16:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can we... How can\Nwe defeat that Black King?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.43,0:16:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or do we even have a chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.33,0:16:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.49,0:16:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.24,0:16:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is a non-zero chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.55,0:16:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's non-zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.83,0:16:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if they join up with\Nthose guys, we still have hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.79,0:16:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Together with the warriors\Nof the deserted castle...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.32,0:16:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...we still have a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.43,0:16:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.82,0:16:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.88,0:16:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.04,0:17:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it! Get 'em, Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.92,0:17:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! Not many bullets left!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.22,0:17:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What on earth?! It's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.22,0:17:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me that. I'm going to destroy Rome.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.14,0:17:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll see about that, old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.60,0:17:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.94,0:17:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do ya have a cigarette?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.40,0:17:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If not, die!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.82,0:17:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're almost at the West Gate. Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.06,0:18:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reporting! Bogie down!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.06,0:18:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Engaging!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.31,0:18:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Target "Dragon"! Target is "Dragon"!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.94,0:18:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanno Naoshi, the commander of\Nthe 301st "Shinsengumi" squadron!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.58,0:18:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think you are?!\NYou disgust me, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.05,0:18:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what the hell\Nis going on here, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.09,0:18:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...crash, you damn scum!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.26,0:18:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Drifter!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.77,0:18:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was a Drifter!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.69,0:18:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never let you get away with this.\NNever! Black King!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.65,0:18:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will be sure to fix your mess!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.82,0:19:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not supposed to exist here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.13,0:19:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too late. You humans\Nare fruit to be cast off.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.05,0:19:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chase them. Seek them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.31,0:19:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find them. Kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.89,0:19:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Drifters won't be allowed to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.66,0:19:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They must be brought to extinction.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.91,0:19:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the mandate of the Inexorable Tribulation.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.38,0:21:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost contact with Grand Master.\NW-What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.20,0:21:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way the Northern Wall\Nwas breached, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.26,0:21:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, that crazy \Ntrio has been acting up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.63,0:21:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What... should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.55,0:21:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew we were being watched.\NWho the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.03,0:21:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I'll get killed!\NIt's a "Leave your head here" ghost!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.90,0:21:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who you calling "ghost"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.28,0:21:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps... a spy?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.28,0:21:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She looks too stupid for that... or maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.16,0:21:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Toyohisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.33,0:21:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.58,0:21:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This girl is speaking Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.00,0:22:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.17,0:22:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you! Tell me! Tell me everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.59,0:22:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Help me! Please don't take my head!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.68,0:22:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't confess,\NI'll let him take care of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.51,0:22:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! I'm Demon King of the Sixth Heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.11,0:22:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My hobby is scorched earth and slaughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.14,0:22:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's make a toast with the skull\Nof a person I killed! Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.82,0:22:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.36,0:22:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm a magician with the\NOctobrist Organization, Olminu.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.82,0:22:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just keeping an eye
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.29,0:22:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,on you Drifters under Grand \NMaster's orders. Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.33,0:22:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell's she saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.91,0:22:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear what the idiot just said?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.71,0:22:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Explain in a way that even\Nthe fool can understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.46,0:22:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's unreasonable.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.54,0:22:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who're you calling fool?!\NDo you want me to take your head?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.50,0:22:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You heard what I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.75,0:22:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you are, as she said,\Na "leave your head here" ghost, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.63,0:22:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... well... it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.97,0:22:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, those like you who \Nare transported from the
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.12,0:22:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,other world are called the "Drifters."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.08,0:22:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our mission as the\N"Octobrist Organization" is...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.94,0:23:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to monitor their activities\Nand to bring them together.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.94,0:23:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you were brought here to fight\Nagainst the people called the "Ends."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.53,0:23:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.53,0:23:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?! Don't make up stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.08,0:23:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nuh-uh.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.66,0:23:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.66,0:23:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.67,0:23:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.88,0:23:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Buddhist Monk"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.09,0:23:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Miracle"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.67,0:23:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Demon King of the Sixth Heaven"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.01,0:23:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Act 4\NActive Heart"
